comments.body:
@windcowles for employment affiliation will you want all available or just the most recent? If all, we'll need to combine them into one column to keep the associations between organization, department, and title. For example:

Option A:
```
Name, orcid, employment affiliation
Anna, xxx, Princeton University / DRDS / Developer; CHF / Library / Developer
```

Option B:
```
Name, orcid, employment organization, department, title
Anna, xxx, Princeton University, DRDS, Developer
```

I guess there's also an Option C which is like Option B but each individual has multiple row entries (one for each employment affiliation)
@hackmastera - we want current Princeton employment and so I think that most recent is probably fine.
